imdb.plot outline: Earth's fallen angels have children and these children have abilities. As an adult, Marcus often struggles with how to use his abilities and often has flashbacks to his teenage years and the place where he and his friends grew up while honing their abilities. He's lost touch with them now but has decided to track them down because of a dream he had that he needs to share with them. He fights some bad guys along the way.
